						<div class="postbody">What about a LUT? For the screen refresh rate you've got 2 possibilities, no? (either it's PAL or it's NTSC)
<br />If the second factor - i.e. number of ticks per measurement interval (1 second?) has a small enough range to result in a table less than a few kB then I'd say use a LUT.</div>

