					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">On paper I'd say the best method would be a combination of those two suggestions:
<br />
<br />1) add up the number of frames for a count of 8 ticks/steps/beats
<br />2) make a look up table (well, one for NTSC one for PAL) based on tepples's calculation using the number from (1) as the index
<br />
<br />I guess the table would have to be 3 bytes per entry: 2 bytes for the whole number part and 1 byte for the fraction?</div>

